{"tid":909024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★Apple已死！蘋果頻頻下調iPhone產量","createTime":"2018-11-20T04:46:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T09:40:12.000Z","uid":19454,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"334f4cbc562e56022ea50bab03a031e74fbcae61","tid":909024,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T04:46:13.000Z","msg":"據知情人士透露，由於蘋果公司(Apple Inc., AAPL)新款iPhone需求低於預期，加上推出更多款iPhone的決定，令蘋果供應鏈陷入混亂，同時亦加大了預測零部件和手機需求的難度。<br />\n<br />\n據悉最近幾周蘋果大幅下調了9月份發布的所有三款iPhone的生產訂單，令蘋果供應商的管理人士及手機和零部件裝配工人倍感沮喪。<br />\n<br />\niPhone XR的前景尤其堪憂。知情人士表示，蘋果之前要求一些供應商在今年9月至明年2月生產大約7,000萬部iPhone XR手機，但到10月末，該公司將這款手機的產量計劃下調了多達三分之一。<br />\n<br />\n其中一些知情人士指出，到上周蘋果向幾家供應商發出通知，再次下調了iPhone XR的產量計劃，主要受智能手機市場日趨飽和以及來自中國手機廠商激烈競爭的影響。蘋果公司對此不予置評。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E9%A0%BB%E9%A0%BB%E4%B8%8B%E8%AA%BFiphone%E7%94%A2%E9%87%8F-%E5%BC%95%E7%99%BC%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E9%8F%88%E6%B7%B7%E4%BA%82%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-020003924.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E8%2598%258B%25E6%259E%259C%25E9%25A0%25BB%25E9%25A0%25BB%25E4%25B8%258B%25E8%25AA%25BFiphone%25E7%2594%25A2%25E9%2587%258F-%25E5%25BC%2595%25E7%2599%25BC%25E4%25BE%259B%25E6%2587%2589%25E9%258F%2588%25E6%25B7%25B7%25E4%25BA%2582%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E9%259A%25AA-020003924.html&d=pYblX2s1qceYPLHhGbA02pZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=074950c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E9%A0%BB%E9%A0%BB%E4%B8%8B%E8%AA%BFiphone%E7%94%A2%E9%87%8F-%E5%BC%95%E7%99%BC%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E9%8F%88%E6%B7%B7%E4%BA%82%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-020003924.html</a>"},{"pid":"25b593555050431c43395b6fdae01e65640012b0","tid":909024,"uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T04:46:32.000Z","msg":"蘋果公司對此不予置評。<br />\n蘋果公司對此不予置評。<br />\n蘋果公司對此不予置評。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\